    0.42055476014509       2    1.21685442265414   -2.68646210106647
                                                    3.03453697205406
    &END 
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 12.0 
  &END POTENTIAL

  &POWELL
     ACCURACY   1.e-14
     STEP_SIZE  0.001
     MAX_INIT   50
     MAX_FUN    100
     STEP_SIZE_SCALING  0.95
     WEIGHT_PSIR0 0.0
     TARGET_POT_SEMICORE      [eV]      0.003000
